                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                            oc:codeContent """from transitleastsquares import transit_mask

# Create transit mask
mask = transit_mask(time, period, duration, t0)
lc_masked = lc[~mask]  # Remove transit points

# Search for second planet
pg_tls2 = tls.transitleastsquares(
    lc_masked.time,
    lc_masked.flux,
    lc_masked.flux_err
)
out_tls2 = pg_tls2.power(period_min=2, period_max=7)
""" ;
